Package org.ro.tuc.pt.model

Class Order

java.lang.Object
org.ro.tuc.pt.model.Order
public class Order
extends java.lang.Object
The class will hold the order data (i.e. id, idClient, idProduct, quantity, price, dateAndTime). It is mapped to a table in the database.
